{"tid":1160448,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"人地唔介意就冇問題 vs 己所不欲，勿施於人；雙重標準","createTime":"2019-05-18T13:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T13:38:12.000Z","uid":238361,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"be9c6d90bbda800c3cb372b4474ec7ab575ac032","tid":1160448,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"我從來唔會稱呼自己女朋友做「條女」，我覺得呢啲係尊重黎 (可能我同我女朋友都一樣咁奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，每次佢地叫我女朋友做「條女」，我都不厭其煩咁糾正佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同佢地講「係女朋友，唔係『條女』」佢地都以膠還膠，應返我「咁條女朋友囉」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n見佢地唔覺得咁叫有問題，我就叫返佢地女朋友做「條女」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我覺得自己好似雙重標準咁，但佢地又唔介意，啫係咁叫唔構成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係一個哲學問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA同B係室友，A開燈瞓唔著，B開燈都瞓得著，所以傾好B深夜唔可以打擾A，而B又唔介意A深夜開燈做嘢，咁A可唔可以 (或者道唔道德) 深夜開燈做嘢？<br />\n<br />\nC同D係室友，C介意D帶女返房扑嘢，D唔介意C帶女返房扑嘢，咁C可唔可以 (或者道唔道德) 帶女返房扑嘢？<br />\n<br />\n諗到頭爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：人地唔介意就冇問題<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：己所不欲，勿施於人；雙重標準"},{"pid":"2969197d19c50f5a13d1047f218b8509aa6d033a","tid":1160448,"uid":238361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"求解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38b4db82365fed02ffb62acb153a2b88b74af6a","tid":1160448,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d4bc321072072bb23fb4116199867f145e74b5df","tid":1160448,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,